ty from Sawa, Level 260 required (MP 128)<font><br><div class="spoiler_header"><a href="javascript:void(0);" onclick="$('#spoiler9984006').toggle();if ($('#spoiler9984006').is(':visible')) $(this).text('SPOILER: Click to hide');else $(this).text('SPOILER: Click to show');" style="display: none;">SPOILER: Click to show</a><span class="sptitle" style="cursor: pointer;" onclick="changespoil(this)"><font><font color="#f209ee">Quest:</font></font></span></div><div class="spoiler" id="spoiler9984006" data-tag="spoiler"><font color="#000000">For SLv2:<br>- Isurugi Statue x1	<br>- Crow Samurai x50, <br>- 2 Bushi Shoulders , <br>- 15 Magic Pill</font><font color="#f209ee" style="color:rgb(242, 9, 238);">.</font></div><font color="#f209ee">More infos:</font></font><br>-Cast time is 1 second at minimum, delay is 1 second too<br>-Paralyzis time is 18 seconds at SLv1 and 20 seconds at SLv3<br>-Damages are affected by <b>MATK and Wind magic</b><br><b></b>-Phantom flame raises Katon's dmg, <b>see PF's "more infos" for full formula (outdated)</b><br>-Still not sure for this one: chances of dealing ailments may be up to DEX <br><br><b><u><font color="#2264f0">Suiton no jutsu:<br></font></u></b>Water element magic attack. Have a chance to freeze the enemy and deals more damages if the enemy is paralyzed and lethargic.<br>Damages goes up too if Astrological Technique is activated and that the enemy is burnt.<br>Level 1 - Quest at Minaula city from Suishin, Level 340 required<font><br><div class="spoiler_header"><a href="javascript:void(0);" onclick="$('#spoiler8130592').toggle();if ($('#spoiler8130592').is(':visible')) $(this).text('SPOILER: Click to hide');else $(this).text('SPOILER: Click to show');" style="display: none;">SPOILER: Click to show</a><span class="sptitle" style="cursor: pointer;" onclick="changespoil(this)"><font color="#f209ee">Quest:</font></span></div><div class="spoiler" id="spoiler8130592" data-tag="spoiler"><font color="#000000">- 10 Water beads<br>- Rabbit Knight ×50<br>- Topnette ×50&nbsp;<br>- Arcarp ×50</font><font color="#f209ee">.</font></div><font color="#f209ee">More infos:</font><br></font>-Cast time is 1 second at minimum, delay is 1<br>-Damages are affected by <b>MATK and Water magic</b><br>-Still not sure for this one: chances of dealing ailments may be up to DEX<br> <br><font color="#c47613"><b><u>Doton no jutsu:</u></b></font><br>Earth element magic attack. Have a chance to make the enemy lethargic and deals more damages if the enemy is paralyzed and burnt.<br>Damages goes up too if Astrological Technique is activated and that the enemy is frozen.<br>Level 1 - Quest at Minaula city from Suishin, Level 340 required<br><div class="spoiler_header"><a href="javascript:void(0);" onclick="$('#spoiler3780051').toggle();if ($('#spoiler3780051').is(':visible')) $(this).text('SPOILER: Click to hide');else $(this).text('SPOILER: Click to show');" style="display: none;">SPOILER: Click to show</a><span class="sptitle" style="cursor: pointer;" onclick="changespoil(this)"><font color="#f209ee">Quest:</font></span></div><div class="spoiler" id="spoiler3780051" data-tag="spoiler"><font color="#000000">- 10 Earth beads<br>- Tigrat ×50<br>- Crystaur ×50<br>- Cochley ×50</font><font color="#f209ee">.</font></div><font color="#f209ee">More infos:<br></font>-Cast time is 1 second at minimum, delay is 1<br>-Damages are affected by <b>MATK and Earth magic</b><br>-Still not sure for this one: chances of dealing ailments may be up to DEX <br><br><u><b>Tenkyoku Jutsu:<br></b></u>Passive skill increasing Jutsus under certain conditions and collect star fragments up to 100. Needed to use Heaven and Earth.&nbsp;<br>Level 1 - Quest at Minaula city from Suishin, Level 340 required<b><br></b><div class="spoiler_header"><a href="javascript:void(0);" onclick="$('#spoiler4942308').toggle();if ($('#spoiler4942308').is(':visible')) $(this).text('SPOILER: Click to hide');else $(this).text('SPOILER: Click to show');" style="display: none;">SPOILER: Click to show</a><span class="sptitle" style="cursor: pointer;" onclick="changespoil(this)"><font color="#f209ee">Quest:</font></span></div><div class="spoiler" id="spoiler4942308" data-tag="spoiler">- Blazing fox ×50&nbsp;<br>- Cane fox ×50<br>- Flametongue ×50&nbsp;<br>- War rooster ×50</div><u><b><br>Tenchi Bansho:<br></b></u>Release the star fragments gathered (100 max).&nbsp;<br>Level 1 - Quest at Minaula city from Suishin, Level 340 and Astrological Technique required.<br><div class="spoiler_header"><a href="javascript:void(0);" onclick="$('#spoiler7824634').toggle();if ($('#spoiler7824634').is(':visible')) $(this).text('SPOILER: Click to hide');else $(this).text('SPOILER: Click to show');" style="display: none;">SPOILER: Click to show</a><span class="sptitle" style="cursor: pointer;" onclick="changespoil(this)"><font color="#f209ee">Quest:</font></span></div><div class="spoiler" id="spoiler7824634" data-tag="spoiler">- 1 crystal of Darkness<br>- 1 spirit bead<br>- 1 bead crystal<br><font color="#f209ee">More infos:</font><br><font color="#000000">-Damages up to MATK. Elemental magic doesnt seem to work consistantly. im investigating ._.</font></div><font color="22f0f0"><b><u><br>E<font color="22c7f0">a</font></u></b></font><font color="22c7f0"><b><u>r<font color="2264f0">t</font></u></b></font><font color="2264f0"><b><u>h</u></b></font><b><u><font color="2264f0">s</font><font color="4b22f0">h</font><font color="#4b22f0"><font color="4b22f0">a</font><font color="b919e6">k</font></font><font color="b919e6">er:<br></font></u></b>Light&amp;Dark element magic attack. Damages go wildly up if the target is burnt and paralyzed. However it will cure the target from these ailments, if those are from your own skills. Total magic pierce when the combo works.<br>Level 1 - Ninja class change (MP 96)<br>Level 2 - Quest at Kakeula city from Ryuan, Level 200 required (MP 160)<br>Level 3 - Quest at Minaula city from Suishin, Level 260 required (MP 224)<font><br><div class="spoiler_header"><a href="javascript:void(0);" onclick="$('#spoiler8797804').toggle();if ($('#spoiler8797804').is(':visible')) $(this).text('SPOILER: Click to hide');else $(this).text('SPOILER: Click to show');" style="display: none;">SPOILER: Click to show</a><span class="sptitle" style="cursor: pointer;" onclick="changespoil(this)"><font><font color="#f209ee">Quest:</font></font></span></div><div class="spoiler" id="spoiler8797804" data-tag="spoiler"><font color="#000000">For SLv2:<br>- 10 Evasion pill&nbsp;<br>- 20 Cracked shield&nbsp;<br>- Lyaph × 50 <br>- Lont mantis × 25 <br><br>For SLv3:<br>- Irai ×1 <br>- Yongo ×50<br>- Utka ×50 <br>- 30 Fertile soil.</font></div><font color="#f209ee">More infos:</font></font><br>-Cast time is 1 second at minimum, delay is 1 second too. <b>-2 seconds delay needed as well.</b><br>-Earthshaker may <b>"spellburst" or "double spellburst"</b>. However, it's <b>equal to half a spellburst and a normal one</b>. It is likely due to its dual element, spellbursting either separately or both at once (according to my tests <a rel="norewrite" target="_blank" href="http://irunaonline.boards.net/thread/17386/double-spell-burst-work-on?page=3">here</a>)<br>-Damages affected by <b>MATK, Light and Dark magic+%</b><br>-Light and/or Dark magic+% from equipments aren't confirmed yet but in any case, it's <b>lower than what it's supposed to be</b> (you won't get 10% more damages from a light drink for example, here is what i've kinda concluded for now:<br>&gt;Against mobs neither Dark or Light, the amount of Light or Dark magic +% supposed to be effective is approximately cut in half<br>&gt;The number of magic +% boost against Light or Dark mobs may vary as:<br>→If using a magic element +% against the same element, it may end up at 25% of what it was supposed to give for the least effective and 50% for the more effective, average of 37.5% of the written number's effectiveness.<br>→If using a magic element +% against the other element, it may end up at 60% of what it was supposed to give for the least effective and 85% for the more effective, average of 72.5% of the written number's effectiveness.)<b><span> <br></span></b><br><b><u>Domination:</u></b><br>Neutral element magic attack. Only available after the use of Earthshaker. Deals great damages and creates 3 clones (like Bunshin) no matter if paralyzed. Damages up with CRT as well.&nbsp;Cancel MP drain from clones and gives a MP regen buff.<br>Level 1 - Quest at Kakeula city from Ryuan, Level 220 requirement (MP 16)<br><font><div class="spoiler_header"><a href="javascript:void(0);" onclick="$('#spoiler2218474').toggle();if ($('#spoiler2218474').is(':visible')) $(this).text('SPOILER: Click to hide');else $(this).text('SPOILER: Click to show');" style="display: none;">SPOILER: Click to show</a><span class="sptitle" style="cursor: pointer;" onclick="changespoil(this)"><font><font color="#f209ee">Quest:</font></font></span></div><div class="spoiler" id="spoiler2218474" data-tag="spoiler"><font color="#000000">- Sakimori no Ryu ×1 <br>- Shiki-oni ×30 <br>- Nozuchi ×60</font><font color="#f209ee">.</font></div><font color="#f209ee">More infos:</font></font><br><b><u>DMG formula:</u></b><br>Domination can only give 10 different DMG (dmg with a 1/2 digit difference excluded, those are probably due to rounded values.)<br>To calculate them, you'll have to get first the Max. DMG, and then you'll deduce the other 9 as follows:<br><br>(MATK×12) × [1+(Neutral magic's percentage amount ÷ 100)] + Fixed magic + CRT×16 = X (result truncated?)<br><br><br>X = Maximum DMG<br><br><br>X-([(MATK×12) ×(1 + (Neutral magic's percentage amount ÷ 100))] ÷ 100)*1 = X1 (results rounded)<br><br>X-([(MATK×12) ×(1 + (Neutral magic's percentage amount ÷ 100))] ÷ 100)*2<br> = X2<br>X-([(MATK×12) ×(1 + (Neutral magic's percentage amount ÷ 100))] ÷ 100)*3<br> = X3<br>X-([(MATK×12) ×(1 + (Neutral magic's percentage amount ÷ 100))] ÷ 100)*4<br> = X4<br>X-([(MATK×12) ×(1 + (Neutral magic's percentage amount ÷ 100))] ÷ 100)*5<br> = X5<br>X-([(MATK×12) ×(1 + (Neutral magic's percentage amount ÷ 100))] ÷ 100)*6<br> = X6<br>X-([(MATK×12) ×(1 + (Neutral magic's percentage amount ÷ 100))] ÷ 100)*7<br> = X7<br>X-([(MATK×12) ×(1 + (Neutral magic's percentage amount ÷ 100))] ÷ 100)*8<br> = X8<br>X-([(MATK×12) ×(1 + (Neutral magic's percentage amount ÷ 100))] ÷ 100)*9<br> = X9<br><br>X, X1, X2, X3, X4, X5, X6, X7, X8 and X9 are all the DMG you can get from Domination!<br><br>-Cast time is 1 second at minimum, delay is 1 second too.&nbsp;<br>-1 CRT = +16 DMG. CRT400= +6400 DMG.<br>-Damages affected by<u> </u><b>MATK, neutral magic+%</b> and CRT&nbsp;<br>-MP heal buff is fixed at 1% MaxMP per second for 10 seconds.<br><br><b><u>Utsusemi:</u></b><br>Passive skill giving a chance to survive with 1 HP when hit to 0 HP. Doen’t work if damages taken are too bigs.<br>Level 1 - Quest at Kakeula city from Ryuan, Level 180 required<br><div class="spoiler_header"><a href="javascript:void(0);" onclick="$('#spoiler621164').toggle();if ($('#spoiler621164').is(':visible')) $(this).text('SPOILER: Click to hide');else $(this).text('SPOILER: Click to show');" style="display: none;">SPOILER: Click to show</a><span class="sptitle" style="cursor: pointer;" onclick="changespoil(this)"><font color="#f209ee">Quest:</font></span></div><div class="spoiler" id="spoiler621164" data-tag="spoiler"><font color="#000000">- Nurikabe ×20 <br>- 20 Vivid plumage&nbsp;<br>- 20 Insect claw&nbsp;<br>- 20 Dango</font><font color="#f209ee">.</font></div><b><u><br>Makibishi:</u></b><br>30 seconds buff that slower the enemy and deals critical damages regularly.<br>Level 1 - Item dropped in Maze of Dendroa (F1 or F3) by Piconi, Level 240 and shuriken mastery Lv2 required. (MP 175)<font color="f209ee"><br>More infos: </font><br>-Also has an <b>AVD+10%</b> effect.<u style="font-weight:bold;"><br></u><br><u style="font-weight:bold;">Swift shadow:</u><br>Passive skill that might prevent a clone from disappearing after